Description:
Nlohmann JSON is used as data container for On Device Model execution internally.
This project is mirrored here from the public GitHub project, with a custom
BUILD.gn to allow for building with our Ninja + GN configuration.
Don't use nlohmann json from chromium or blink code, but use base/values.h,
base/json, and third_party/blink/platform/json (for blink) instead.

